---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'

const updated = '2026-06-20'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Disclaimer — oriz · cards"
  description="What cards.oriz.in is and isn't."
>
  <div class="spine-prose">
    <header class="page-head">
      <p class="eyebrow mono">
        <a href="/">cards</a> / <a href="/legal/">legal</a> / disclaimer
      </p>
      <h1>disclaimer</h1>
      <p class="meta">Last updated: {updated}</p>
    </header>

    <article class="prose">
      <p>
        Everything on cards.oriz.in is published in good faith for general
        information only. Use it at your own risk.
      </p>

      <h2>Not financial advice</h2>
      <p>
        The card profiles, fees, rewards rates, and eligibility criteria on
        cards.oriz.in are reference data assembled from public sources. They
        are <strong>not</strong> investment, tax, or insurance advice, and they
        are <strong>not</strong> a recommendation to apply for or use any
        particular card.
      </p>
      <p>
        Card terms change. The fee, interest rate, reward rate, or feature on
        this site may be out of date or wrong. <strong>Always verify on the
        issuing bank's own website</strong> before applying or relying on a
        benefit. Consult a SEBI-registered investment advisor for financial
        decisions.
      </p>
      <p>
        oriz, its operator, and its contributors do not recommend, endorse,
        or assume responsibility for any card, bank, or financial product
        discussed on this site.
      </p>

      <h2>Not legal advice</h2>
      <p>
        Articles touching on tax, regulation, or compliance reflect the
        author's reading of the rules at the time of writing. Rules change.
        Verify with your own counsel before acting.
      </p>

      <h2>External links</h2>
      <p>
        We link to third-party sites — including issuing banks — that we find
        useful. We don't control their content, and inclusion is not an
        endorsement.
      </p>

      <h2>Affiliate disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        cards.oriz.in does not currently use affiliate links. If that ever
        changes, such links will be marked clearly. The choice of which cards
        we list is never influenced by referral economics.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
